snippet.title: Playground VR - Trailer 2021
snippet.description:
Playground VR It is an open-world game where you can experience the beautiful essence of VR. 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1504100/Playground_VR/

Oculus: Soon
VIVEPORT: Soon


Do you want to fly a balloon? Fly! Are you not afraid to be cured of cannon? Launch yourself! Do you want to take to the sea waves? Swim! Do you want to climb the building? Free way! Yes, you can do it all!
